# What `gcloud builds submit` / `run deploy --source` UPLOAD as build context.
# Without this, gcloud uploads everything here — including the ~1 GB local .venv.
# Keep: app/, scripts/, pyproject.toml, uv.lock, Dockerfile*.
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.env
.env.*
omni_out/
*.pt
.git/
node_modules/
